description: Owned and operated by two former Peace Corps travelers, Kargi Gogo specializes in bringing food from the country Georgia to the people of Portland! Menu items include authentic traditional Georgian dishes like their Khachapuri (Georgian cheese bread), Khinkali (stuffed dumplings), and their Badrijiana (eggplant, walnut and garlic rolls.) Grab a dish or try a bit of everything!
name: Kargi Gogo
